OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776243304
OL,3,CUK youth unemployment is 'social
OL,4,Cdisaster', says man appointed to fix
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FThe UK's youth unemployment crisis is
OL,8,Fa "social disaster", says the ex-
OL,9,Fminister appointed by Sir Keir Starmer
OL,10,Fto try to fix the problem.
OL,12,FAlan Milburn, a former MP who was a
OL,13,Fminister in Tony Blair's government,
OL,14,Fwas recruited by the current Labour
OL,15,Fgovernment to assess why almost one
OL,16,Fmillion young people are not in
OL,17,Femployment, education, or training
OL,18,F(Neets).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776243304
OL,3,CUK youth unemployment is 'social
OL,4,Cdisaster', says man appointed to fix
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,F"This is a big problem. It's a
OL,8,Fnational crisis," he told ITV News,
OL,9,F"And the real problem is this; 60% of
OL,10,Fthem, six and ten of them, are
OL,11,Feconomically inactive. That means
OL,12,Fthey're not even looking for work."
OL,14,FThe number of 16 to 24-year-olds Neets
OL,15,Fis at its highest level for over
OL,16,F10years, "and it's getting worse, not
OL,17,Fgetting better," Milburn said.
OL,19,FHow is the government addressing the
OL,20,Fproblem?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776243304
OL,3,CUK youth unemployment is 'social
OL,4,Cdisaster', says man appointed to fix
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FSeveral schemes to address the problem
OL,8,Fhave already been announced by the
OL,9,Fgovernment, ahead of Milburn's review
OL,10,Fbeing published in the summer, but he
OL,11,Fsays they are "subscale at the moment".
OL,13,FThe Youth Jobs Grant and Jobs
OL,14,FGuarantee, beginning in spring, will
OL,15,Fsee the government fund work
OL,16,Fplacements or pay firms to hire young
OL,17,Fpeople who have been unemployed and on
OL,18,Fbenefits for either more than six
OL,19,Fmonths or 18 months.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776243304
OL,3,CUK youth unemployment is 'social
OL,4,Cdisaster', says man appointed to fix
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FAlong with a plan for additional
OL,8,Fapprenticeships, the government says
OL,9,Fits youth unemployment schemes will
OL,10,Fcreate 200,000 jobs and placements.
OL,12,F"It's a really good start, but it's
OL,13,Fonly a start," Milburn said. "We've
OL,14,Fgot to make sure that it is more
OL,15,Fwidely available."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776243304
OL,3,CUK youth unemployment is 'social
OL,4,Cdisaster', says man appointed to fix
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FHigh youth unemployment is "not a new
OL,8,Fphenomenon" and has "been going on for
OL,9,Fa very long time", Milburn told ITV
OL,10,FNews - but critics of the government,
OL,11,Fincluding Reform UK and the
OL,12,FConservatives, say Labour has made the
OL,13,Fproblem worse.
OL,15,FThey claim Labour is discouraging
OL,16,Fbusinesses from hiring young people by
OL,17,Fincreasing minimum wage and business
OL,18,Frates.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776243304
OL,3,CUK youth unemployment is 'social
OL,4,Cdisaster', says man appointed to fix
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FWhen asked about those claims, Milburn
OL,8,Fappeared to accept that the policies
OL,9,Fdo increase the risk for companies
OL,10,Fhiring young people, but said youth
OL,11,Funemployment has been an issue long
OL,12,Fbefore Labour came to power.
OL,14,FWhy is youth unemployment so high?
OL,16,FHe said the root cause is a much more
OL,17,Fcomplex mix, pointing to the link with
OL,18,Fsocial disadvantage, mental health,
OL,19,Fphysical health, and a lack of hope
OL,20,Famong young people.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776243304
OL,3,CUK youth unemployment is 'social
OL,4,Cdisaster', says man appointed to fix
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,F"The parts of the country that have
OL,8,Fgot the highest levels of being native
OL,9,Fplaces like Middlesbrough, Hartlepool,
OL,10,FKnowsley - some of the most
OL,11,Fdisadvantaged places in the country.
OL,12,FBut the new kid on the block, so to
OL,13,Fspeak, is what is going on with
OL,14,Fpeople's health.
OL,16,F"So 50% of young people who are not in
OL,17,Feducation, employment and training are
OL,18,Freporting a health condition, very
OL,19,Foften a mental health condition on
OL,20,Fneurodiversity, ADHD and autism".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776243304
OL,3,CUK youth unemployment is 'social
OL,4,Cdisaster', says man appointed to fix
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FHe does not accept the claim that
OL,8,Fmental health conditions are over-
OL,9,Fdiagnosed in the UK, but said that
OL,10,Fwork is good for mental health.
OL,12,FHe said: "What's happening is the
OL,13,Fdiagnosis levels are rising and all
OL,14,Ftoo often what happens is then the
OL,15,Fstate comes along and says, 'you've
OL,16,Fgot a problem. You can't work'. Rather
OL,17,Fthan helping people to be able to
OL,18,Fwork."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776243304
OL,3,CUK youth unemployment is 'social
OL,4,Cdisaster', says man appointed to fix
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,F"Work is good for your mental health,
OL,8,Fnot bad," he added. "Being out of work
OL,9,Fis disastrous for your mental health."
OL,11,F'The UK doesn't have a jobs shortage,
OL,12,Fit has a hope shortage' - is
OL,13,FArtificial Intelligence to blame?
OL,15,FWhen ITV News has spoken to young
OL,16,Fpeople looking for work, most of them
OL,17,Ftalk about applying for dozens of jobs
OL,18,Fand never hearing anything back.
OL,20,FMany of them say it leaves them
OL,21,Ffeeling hopeless about the future.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776243304
OL,3,CUK youth unemployment is 'social
OL,4,Cdisaster', says man appointed to fix
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FMilburn has found the same while
OL,8,Fconducting his review.
OL,10,F"The biggest thing that's in short
OL,11,Fsupply in the country is not jobs. The
OL,12,Fbiggest thing is hope," he said,
OL,13,Fadding that "it must be the most
OL,14,Fdemoralising thing to apply sometimes
OL,15,Ffor dozens, sometimes, frankly, for
OL,16,Fhundreds of jobs but not hear back."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776243304
OL,3,CUK youth unemployment is 'social
OL,4,Cdisaster', says man appointed to fix
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FAnd he thinks AI could be at least
OL,8,Fpartly to blame - but not for taking
OL,9,Fhuman jobs, which is another concern.
OL,10,FHe believes employers are relying too
OL,11,Fmuch on AI to sift through
OL,12,Fapplications.
OL,14,F"A lot of the problem now is that a
OL,15,Flot of the responses that the
OL,16,Femployers are generating, if they're
OL,17,Fgenerating any, when it comes to young
OL,18,Fpeople applying, it's all done by
OL,19,Falgorithms.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776243304
OL,3,CUK youth unemployment is 'social
OL,4,Cdisaster', says man appointed to fix
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,F"It's not done by a human being. The
OL,8,Fapplications come in. It's all AI
OL,9,Fsorted, etc. so human beings never see
OL,10,Fthe application from another human
OL,11,Fbeing."
OL,13,FHe said the government should
OL,14,Fencourage employers to respond to
OL,15,Ffailed applicants, but "it's really
OL,16,Fdifficult to mandate that businesses
OL,17,Fdo it".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776243304
OL,3,CUK youth unemployment is 'social
OL,4,Cdisaster', says man appointed to fix
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FOn the risk of AI taking human jobs,
OL,8,Fhe said: "There's no doubt that it
OL,9,Fwill impact some forms of employment,
OL,10,Fbut equally it will create new forms
OL,11,Fof employment as well.
OL,13,F"That's what's happened with every
OL,14,Ftechnical digital revolution that the
OL,15,Fworld has ever seen. There's some
OL,16,Flosers, some winners. What we've got
OL,17,Fto do is maximise the winners."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31714
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776243304
OL,3,CUK youth unemployment is 'social
OL,4,Cdisaster', says man appointed to fix
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FHe said it is a "social disaster" to
OL,8,Fhave so many young people out of work,
OL,9,Fadding: "We all pay the price if you
OL,10,Fhave a million young people who are
OL,11,Fnot in education, employment and
OL,12,Ftraining."
OL,14,F"We pay the price socially with a more
OL,15,Ffractured society, and we pay the
OL,16,Fprice economically because we're not
OL,17,Fgetting the talent and potential that
OL,18,Fthose young people have."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
